title: [SOLVED] 820-2914-b no trackpad and no keyboard usb keyboard an trackpad works
message: Either bad trackpad & trackpad cable or bad U5701. Check R5704 to make sure 3.3v is present on both sides. Keyboard won't work if trackpad is bad on this model in my experience.
